Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration for completing 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average delay in starting 'Accepted + Assigned' after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Earliest start time for 'Accepted + Assigned' after 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Latest completion time of 'Accepted + Assigned' before 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Duration comparison between 'Accepted + Assigned' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' in the most frequent process variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' in any case
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Assigned' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' leading to 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration distribution of 'Accepted + Assigned' for cases with high impact

Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
